i-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">8</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月，受国家煤矿安全监察局委托，陕西煤矿安全监察局批复陕西彬长矿业集团有限公司文家坡矿井安全设施设计。矿井设计能力<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">400</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">万吨<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">/</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></font></td>","createTime":1518425013561,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局安全监察司","pubTime":1471449600000,"region":["陕西省"],"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"内蒙古平庄煤业（集团）有限责任公司玻璃沟矿井、陕西彬长矿业集团有限公司文家坡矿井通过安全设施设计审查","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5480/2016/0818/274614/content_274614.htm"}
