{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>公告公文","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于征求</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">《煤矿特种作业人员安全技术</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">培训大纲</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">及考核要求（征求意见稿）》意见的函</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">65号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全培训主管部门，各省级煤矿安全监察局，有关中央企业：<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局组织修订了《煤矿特种作业人员安全技术培训大纲及考核要求（征求意见稿）》（见附件，可从国家煤矿安全监察局政府网站“公告公文”栏目下载），现征求各单位意见。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">请各省级煤矿安全培训主管部门组织本辖区煤矿企业研究提出修改意见，各省级煤矿安全监察局组织所属监察分局研究提出修改意见，并于<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2018</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">30</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日前将书面意见连同电子版一并反馈国家煤矿安监局行管司。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n           <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">联系人及电话：潘霄，<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">010-64464064</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（带传真）；<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.