{"authors":"李静","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>要闻","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n ﻿  \n <meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"Content-Type\"> \n <meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"MSHTML 8.00.6001.23642\"> \n <style>@font-face {\r\n\tfont-family: 宋体;\r\n}\r\n@font-face {\r\n\tfont-family: 宋体;\r\n}\r\n@font-face {\r\n\tfont-family: Calibri;\r\n}\r\n@font-face {\r\n\tfont-family: @宋体;\r\n}\r\n@page WordSection1 {size: 595.3pt 841.9pt; margin: 72.0pt 90.0pt 72.0pt 90.0pt; layout-grid: 15.6pt; }\r\nP.MsoNormal {\r\n\tTEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\r\n}\r\nLI.MsoNormal {\r\n\tTEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\r\n}\r\nDIV.MsoNormal {\r\n\tTEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\r\n}\r\n.MsoChpDefault {\r\n\tFONT-FAMILY: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\r\n}\r\nDIV.WordSection1 {\r\n\tpage: WordSection1\r\n}\r\n</style>   \n <div style=\"LAYOUT-GRID:  15.6pt none\" class=\"WordSection1\"> \n  <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 15.6pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;12<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">21<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">日，国家煤矿安监局法律顾问制度启动会议在京举行，国家安全监管总局副局长、国家煤矿安监局局长黄玉治为北京大学法学院教授邵景春、中央财经大学法律事务办公室主任李轩颁发法律顾问聘书，国家煤矿安监局副局长桂来保出席会议。</span></span></span></span></p> \n  <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 15.6pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">会议指出，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">建立法律顾问制度是落实中共中央办公厅、国务院办公厅《关于推行法律顾问制度和公职律师公司律师制度的意见》的具体举措，将为国家煤矿安监局重大行政决策制定、监察执法、事故调查、复议应诉、审查重要合同协议等工作提供有力法律支撑，为推进国家煤矿安监局依法行政发挥重要积极作用。</span></span></p> \n  <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 15.6pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">国家煤矿安监局有关司室负责人参加会议，并研讨相关具体事项。</span></p> \n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n </div> \n</div>","createTime":1518425018129,"modules":[],"pubSource":"事故调查司","pubTime":1513872000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家煤矿安监局建立法律顾问制度","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/1222/300070/content_300070.htm"}
{"authors":"李振营","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>公告公文","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于报送<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年度<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">煤矿安全培训考核工作总结材料的通知<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">58号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全培训主管部门，有关涉煤中央企业：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">请各单位认真汇总<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年度煤矿“三项岗位人员”安全培训考核发证监督检查情况，总结煤矿安全培训工作经验，分析存在的主要问题，提出加强和改进煤矿安全培训工作的意见建议，形成总结报告，并填报<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年<span lang=\"EN-US\">1-10月煤矿“三项岗位人员”安全培训情况和<span lang=\"EN-US\">11-12月计划培训人数、煤矿主要负责人和安全生产管理人员考核情况统计表（附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">1、<span lang=\"EN-US\">2、<span lang=\"EN-US\">3，有关涉煤中央企业不填），于<span lang=\"EN-US\">12月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10日前将总结报告及表格以传真和电子邮件方式报送至国家煤矿安监局行业管理司（报表格式电子版在国家煤矿安全监察局政府网站“公告公文”栏目下载）。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n              <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">联系人及电话：潘霄，<span lang=\"EN-US\">010-64464064（带传真）；<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">电子邮箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\">panx@chinasafety.gov.cn。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">附件：<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20171127fujian1.xls\" target=\"_blank\">煤矿主要负责人和安全生产管理人员安全培训情况统计表</a>&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 80pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 5.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\"><a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20171127fujian2.xls\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">煤矿特种作业人员安全培训情况统计表</span></a>&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 80pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 5.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">3.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-